{
  "id": "69ec1b02b44ffd1437cebaaf",
  "title": "行動遡行",
  "created": 1777081092,
  "updated": 1777081105,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69ec1b02b44ffd1437cebaaf",
      "text": "行動遡行",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777081092,
      "updated": 1777081092
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec1b0300000000007453a3",
      "text": " [行動遡行]とは、1つ前の行動を思い出す、それを繰り返してどんどん時間を遡っていくこと",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777081092,
      "updated": 1777081092
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec1b0300000000007453a4",
      "text": " 例えば、いまお風呂にいるとしたら",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777081092,
      "updated": 1777081092
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec1b0300000000007453a5",
      "text": "  お風呂に入る前に脱衣所で服を脱いだ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777081092,
      "updated": 1777081092
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec1b0300000000007453a6",
      "text": "  その前にトイレに行った",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777081092,
      "updated": 1777081092
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec1b0300000000007453a7",
      "text": "  その前に髪をとかした",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777081092,
      "updated": 1777081092
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec1b0300000000007453a8",
      "text": "  その前に部屋から移動して脱衣所に服を持って行った",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777081092,
      "updated": 1777081092
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec1b0300000000007453a9",
      "text": "  その前に……",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777081092,
      "updated": 1777081092
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec1b0e00000000007453aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777081102,
      "updated": 1777081102
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec1b0e00000000007453ab",
      "text": "知った場所",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777081102,
      "updated": 1777081105
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec1b0e00000000007453ac",
      "text": " どこだっけ[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777081102,
      "updated": 1777081105
    },
    {
      "id": "69ec1b0e00000000007453ad",
      "text": " 心の調子を良くするものとしてWeb記事で紹介されていた気がする",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777081102,
      "updated": 1777081105
    }
  ]
}